import { Segment,Grid,Form,Header } from 'semantic-ui-react';

export default (props) => {
    return (<Segment>
        <Grid>
            <Grid.Row>
                <Header as='h3'>Pottyng</Header>
            </Grid.Row>
            <Grid.Row>
                <Form>
                    <Form.Group>
                        <Form.Group>
                            <Form.Checkbox label='Peed' />
                            <Form.Checkbox label='Pooped' />
                        </Form.Group>
                        <Form.TextArea label='Notes' placeholder='Potty Notes' />
                    </Form.Group>
                </Form>  
            </Grid.Row>
            <Grid.Row>
                <Header as='h3'>Feeding</Header>
            </Grid.Row>
            <Grid.Row>
                <Form>
                    <Form.Checkbox label='Ate' />
                    <Form.TextArea label='Notes' placeholder='Feeding Notes' />
                </Form>    
            </Grid.Row>
            <Grid.Row>
                <Header as='h3'>Training</Header>
            </Grid.Row>
            <Grid.Row>
                <Form>
                    <Form.Checkbox label='Ate' />
                    <Form.TextArea label='Notes' placeholder='Feeding Notes' />
                </Form>  
            </Grid.Row>
        </Grid>
        
    </Segment>)
}
